). Half of tergite IX missing, other half with about 7 setae. Gonocoxite with 10 setae. Cercus 105 m long. Seminal capsule 71 m long, 53 m wide. Spermathecal ducts nearly straight. Gonapophysis VIII divided, with large ventrolateral (
Fig. 18
